    • Field Detail

      • MAP_PLAYLISTS

        public static final String MAP_PLAYLISTS
        Map key to obtain playlists for a track.

        This is a column definition, but is not displayed as such. It holds playlist names that are displayed on the right side of a split pane when the results of a track query are displayed.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MAP_BYPASSED

        public static final String MAP_BYPASSED
        Map key to obtain bypassed playlists for a track.

        This is a column definition, but is not displayed as such.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Track t2)
        Compares a given track to this track, used for sorting. We sort by track name.
        Parameters:
        t2 - track to be compared to this track
        Returns:
        negative value, zero, or positive value to indicate less than, equal to, or greater than, respectively
